DATA.virtual_field_sql_1:
CASE WHEN status_effort_fcast = 3 THEN 'signal_red '
     WHEN status_effort_fcast = 2 THEN 'signal_yellow '
     ELSE '' END
|| CASE WHEN effort_fcast_d > effort_fcast AND effort_fcast > 0.0 THEN 'demand_overload effort_overbooked '
        WHEN effort_fcast_d < effort_fcast AND effort_fcast_d > 0.0 THEN 'demand_incomplete '
        ELSE '' END
|| CASE WHEN effort_fcast_a > effort_fcast_d AND effort_fcast_d > 0.0 THEN 'assignment_overload demand_overbooked '
        WHEN effort_fcast_a > effort_fcast AND effort_fcast > 0.0 THEN 'assignment_overload effort_overbooked '
        WHEN effort_fcast_a < effort_fcast_d AND effort_fcast_a > 0.0 THEN 'assignment_incomplete '
        WHEN effort_fcast_a < effort_fcast AND effort_fcast_a > 0.0 THEN 'assignment_incomplete '
        ELSE '' END
|| CASE WHEN effort_act > effort_fcast AND effort_fcast > 0.0 THEN 'actual_overload '
        WHEN effort_act > effort_fcast_a AND effort_fcast_a > 0.0 THEN 'actual_overload '
        WHEN effort_act > 0.0 AND effort_fcast_a = 0.0 AND effort_fcast_a = 0.0 THEN 'actual_overload '
        ELSE '' END
